      "Etapa 6: avance até NG++/Drangleic Castle para comprar magias, milagres e piromancias restantes com Chancellor Wellager, além de fechar Master of Sorcery, Master of Miracles e Master of Pyromancy.",
      "Etapa 7: faça cleanup final de covenants, spells, hexes, gestures, Lucatiel, Benhart, NPC questlines, Gathering of Exiles, equipamentos herdados e a platina The Dark Soul."
